title: BRIEF-WSE suspends Nemex SA trading
text:
BRIEF-WSE suspends Nemex SA trading Sept 14 
Sept 14 Warsaw Stock Exchange (WSE): 
* Said on Friday that it resolved to suspend Nemex SA trading of shares on NewConnect market as of Sept. 14 Source text: bit.ly/1NrqSC1
